I'm ready to help you search and analyze the dealerflow codebase. I understand that I'm in READ-ONLY mode and can only search, grep, and read files without making any modifications.

I have the context from CLAUDE.md about the test drive form requirements:
- Remove make/model fields if VRM is matched
- Remove license-related fields
- Remove insurance fields
- Adjust test drive details (set date to today, time to current, remove mileage/fuel/staff fields)
- Remove return details fields

I'm prepared to help you find and analyze code related to any aspect of this dealerflow application. What would you like me to search for or analyze?
